name: Vision HERO Multiply Guy
desc: If you take battle or effect damage: You can place this card from your GY face-up in your Spell & Trap Zone as a Continuous Trap. During the Main Phase, while this card is treated as a Continuous Trap: You can Tribute 1 "HERO" monster; Special Summon this card. If this card is Special Summoned from the Spell & Trap Zone: You can have 1 monster on the field gain 800 ATK. You can only use each effect of "Vision HERO Multiply Guy" once per turn.
